Class UserImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • implementations.UserImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    User

    public class UserImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements User
    This class represents a known User of in a Calendar. Users should only be created by the CalendarImpl itself and can not exist without its context. If an UserImpl is removed from its calendar, it becomes invalid and should not be used anymore.
